entries.femaleVariant: An' he fuckin' calls and asks how everything's going, how I'm doin', how I like the new team.
Yeah, like suddenly we're chooms or something. Just cause my leg gonked on me, 'cause they dumped me where nobody else wanted to work.
Fuck 'im. One of those assholes, gets off on other people's misery.
I mean, I sorta knew the job'd be full of pricks just like him, no surprise there...
But all the fuckin' games, y'know? Like we chooms... I can't! Rather have some gonk just say it to my face so I could fuckin' punch his.
Could always send a few mercs after 'im.
Haha, know what? Not a bad idea, that.
